caption: (I picked this song because it's Tay's favorite) anyways, when I met Taylor (3rd time) he remembered that I used to have braces, and I cried. But he told me a little about magcon and he told me stuff that him and Cam keep bringing up when they talk about it. I can't tell you guys anything. But you guys will be so excited! Just wait until November!! I'm so excited myself! I'm not some special insider guys. Like I legit just asked him and he told me a lot of stuff that was on his mind about it. And I'm hoping you guys will freak out when he tells the rest of you guys!!!!!! Hope everyone has a great day!❤️
